  <h2>The concept</h2>
  <p>
    THE CLUB is designed as a practical, high-impact facility for real people:
    tradies, shift workers, athletes and locals who want better recovery, less
    stress and improved performance. The space combines:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Infrared and traditional sauna options</li>
    <li>Steam room and heat therapy zones</li>
    <li>Dedicated ice bath and contrast therapy area</li>
    <li>Strength and conditioning zone</li>
    <li>Spaces for breath work, mindset and downtime</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Why Pakenham?</h2>
  <p>
    Pakenham and the surrounding Cardinia growth corridor are experiencing rapid
    population growth, an increase in younger families and a strong base of
    tradies and workers who value fitness and lifestyle ‚Äì but have limited
    access to dedicated recovery spaces.
  </p>
  <p>
    THE CLUB aims to become the go-to destination for recovery, performance and
    mental reset in the region.
  </p>

  <h2>Business model (high level)</h2>
  <div class="card">
    <ul>
      <li><span class="highlight">Memberships:</span> tiered weekly/fortnightly memberships with different access levels.</li>
      <li><span class="highlight">Casual passes:</span> drop-in and multi-visit passes for non-members.</li>
      <li><span class="highlight">Small group sessions:</span> guided contrast therapy, breath work and recovery classes.</li>
      <li><span class="highlight">Add-ons:</span> potential for massage, bodywork and performance coaching partners.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

